Feel the thrill of luxury and speed with the Lamborghini live wallpaper, transforming your Chrome new tab into a showcase of this iconic supercar.

The Lamborghini Live Wallpaper features the sleek design and raw power of this legendary car, giving car enthusiasts a visually stunning experience every time they open a new tab.

Features:
Lamborghini Live Wallpaper
Google search bar
Addable and removable shortcuts
Date and time display

This Chrome extension offers a stunning chrome wallpaper alongside practical features to enhance your browsing. As one of the top chrome live wallpapers, it upgrades your chrome background with luxury and performance.
